# Backup grafana data every day
0 1 * * * <%= Rubber.root %>/script/rubber cron --task util:backup --directory /mnt/grafana_backups --name grafana --command "nice zip \%dir\%/\%name\%_<%= rubber_env.host %>_\%time_stamp\%.zip /mnt/grafana"
